00:32:19.310 --> 00:32:21.530
Magic!

00:32:21.530 --> 00:32:24.410
The prior, 1/5 for each, right?

00:32:24.410 --> 00:32:26.030
That's where we're
starting from.

00:32:26.030 --> 00:32:27.400
We roll a 5.

00:32:27.400 --> 00:32:28.890
That's our likelihood.

00:32:28.890 --> 00:32:31.410
Again, you get a
